en_177467_0	Police have arrested 2 gramaseva officers who had in their possession 3 pendants which were made with ivory.
en_177467_1	The suspects were arrested this evening (02) following a tip-off received by Nikawaratiya Division's Intelligence Unit.
en_177467_2	They were arrested in Polpithigama.
en_177467_3	The 2 gramaseva officers have been arrested based on information provided by the suspects who are in remand custody over the killing of 'Dala Poottuwa' tusker.
en_177467_4	The suspects will be produced before Mahawa Magistrate tomorrow.
